  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/6b244d4ddc57a6e0ae5e4eb76f9021d8.webp?t=1724150260\" width=500 height=47 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the desolate land of the future!</strong></h2><br>In this adventure you will have to correct the mistakes of mankind and rebuild a devastated planet. Your main task will be to restore the atmosphere, normalize the temperature on the surface and get rid of the radiation interfering with the vegetation!<br><br>You will play as a robot model TRF 7, created to return the planet to its original form, after a global catastrophe completely destroyed all life on earth.<br><br><strong>Survive, collect resources and craft items you need!</strong><br>You will have to explore the planet, find the necessary resources and open new crafts. Each item found in the world is unique and will not be renewed, will you have enough to restore the planet?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/1c152e1ba70ab99870a60a38808c02ff.poster.avif?t=1724150260\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/1c152e1ba70ab99870a60a38808c02ff.webm?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/1c152e1ba70ab99870a60a38808c02ff.mp4?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Build outposts and bases</strong><br>Do all the items you find need to be stored somewhere? Great, because you can build a base to your liking and place everything you need on it: resource chests, crafters, upgrade tools and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/a4d9bfb3ac0c2f179089b7052a2232f6.poster.avif?t=1724150260\" width=690 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/a4d9bfb3ac0c2f179089b7052a2232f6.webm?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/a4d9bfb3ac0c2f179089b7052a2232f6.mp4?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Energy is very important!</strong><br>Each mechanism runs on electricity, and you have to run a cable to it to connect the mains...and it's fun!<br><br><strong>Best of all: watch the planet change in real time!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/fe5674485fe2e0f03a85840ad5ad3862.poster.avif?t=1724150260\" width=640 height=317 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/fe5674485fe2e0f03a85840ad5ad3862.webm?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/e7159112a2fcb56df6ad55783c6a1e91.avif?t=1724150260\" width=374 height=448 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/6b244d4ddc57a6e0ae5e4eb76f9021d8.webp?t=1724150260\" width=500 height=47 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the desolate land of the future!</strong></h2><br>In this adventure you will have to correct the mistakes of mankind and rebuild a devastated planet. Your main task will be to restore the atmosphere, normalize the temperature on the surface and get rid of the radiation interfering with the vegetation!<br><br>You will play as a robot model TRF 7, created to return the planet to its original form, after a global catastrophe completely destroyed all life on earth.<br><br><strong>Survive, collect resources and craft items you need!</strong><br>You will have to explore the planet, find the necessary resources and open new crafts. Each item found in the world is unique and will not be renewed, will you have enough to restore the planet?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/1c152e1ba70ab99870a60a38808c02ff.poster.avif?t=1724150260\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/1c152e1ba70ab99870a60a38808c02ff.webm?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/1c152e1ba70ab99870a60a38808c02ff.mp4?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Build outposts and bases</strong><br>Do all the items you find need to be stored somewhere? Great, because you can build a base to your liking and place everything you need on it: resource chests, crafters, upgrade tools and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/a4d9bfb3ac0c2f179089b7052a2232f6.poster.avif?t=1724150260\" width=690 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/a4d9bfb3ac0c2f179089b7052a2232f6.webm?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/a4d9bfb3ac0c2f179089b7052a2232f6.mp4?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Energy is very important!</strong><br>Each mechanism runs on electricity, and you have to run a cable to it to connect the mains...and it's fun!<br><br><strong>Best of all: watch the planet change in real time!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/fe5674485fe2e0f03a85840ad5ad3862.poster.avif?t=1724150260\" width=640 height=317 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/fe5674485fe2e0f03a85840ad5ad3862.webm?t=1724150260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097690/extras/e7159112a2fcb56df6ad55783c6a1e91.avif?t=1724150260\" width=374 height=448 /></span>",
